  <summary>12/11/2014--Introduced.
Honors the 100th Anniversary of the World War I Christmas Truce of 1914, and recognizes the Truce's symbol of the triumph of the human spirit over adversity.

 Commemorates the Christmas Truce of 1914 and its legacy as a message of future peace and unity between all nations.</summary>
